import React from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet, TouchableOpacity } from 'react-native';

export default function Navbar({ onCategorySelect }) {
  return (
    <View style={styles.navbar}>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Home')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Home</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Men')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Men</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Women')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Women</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Electronics')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Electronics</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Kids')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Kids</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Home-Decor')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Home-Decor</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => onCategorySelect('Profile')}>
        <Text style={styles.navItem}>Profile</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
      <View style={styles.logo}>
        <Text style={styles.logoText}>KMART</Text>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
}

// Rest of the styles remain the same
